TEXT.S: Dave Annable kawas tay 1979, ryax sa tay 15 nqu tay 9, Dave Annable, squliq na Bunge'. qnxan nya Annable htgan beh Suffern,New York sazing sen mopu kawas (2010) kekong.hiya mrkyas beh New,York na Walden qalang, maki qasa hiya mzyu mari ru mari. hiya yaba kyokya ru yotay lamu. Annable mqwas beh Valley Central pqwasan biru,masoq beh 1997 kawas. hiya mqwas beh New York(SUNY Plattsburgh) kruhu' pqwasan biru. cyux maki qasa,hiya tmwang seto na (PSTV) telivi.pincyagan nya ru . hiya cingay , Late Night with Dave Annable, Cardinal Sports ru The Roommate Game maki PSTV. kawas 2003,Annable kahul krahu' pqwasan biru mhngaw la. mshriq New York SUNY, Plattsburgh, Annable ru Richard Pinter mcbaq ,maki New York . pincyogan nya 2002 kawas,Annable te qutux mhtuw maki NBC.Annable mhtuw maki cingay ,A Mountain Dew,Starburst ru Abercrombie, Fitch. 2004 kawas,Annable mhtuw films Little Black ru Spellbound maki ega. huy2005 kawas 9 byacing, Annable t'aring mhtuw Aaron Lewis maki telivi Fox Reunion,qani Fox kmal tzyu rangi nya tmwang hiya te 20 pqwasan hlahuy,qutux mhuqil ,kwara squilq squilq. 12 byacing, Fox maki te qeru mhtuw lga, ini mhtuw la.maki sinbung,cinbwanan hiya ga wanglu mhtuw blaq na , ini . 2006 kawas, Annable ru Calista Flockhart, Rachel Griffithsru Sally Field msqun mhtuw ABC telivi mhtuw Justin Walker,telivi qani qutux . 2007 kawas, Annable ga qutux mlikuy te pitu maki squilq . 2008 kawas, Annable magal na cingay ,blaq .qani pspung magal pspung 2011 kawas. 2012 kawas 1 byacing Annable Rachael Taylor , Vanessa Williams ru Robert Buckley msqun mhtuw ABC 666 mlikuy mincyogun nya
